data.description: Discover this charming 2 bdrm, 1 bath oasis located conveniently near the intersection of 33rd Ave & Division St. This property offers potential galore with a little TLC & a minor upgrade, this house could be a dream home! Spacious 2 car garage, perfect for oversized vehicles or extra storage. Ideal for all, whether you are a first time home buyer or an astute investor, this property presents a golden opportunity. Don't let this chance slip away! Explore the potential of this property & turn it into your dream oasis.
